WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.666 --> 00:00:06.166
Who's knocking on the door in broad daylight?

2
00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:08.800
Shenyang, hurry up, I'm worried, you can hide first

3
00:00:15.533 --> 00:00:17.833
Who are you looking for?

4
00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:19.566
It doesn't seem to be from the village.

5
00:00:19.666 --> 00:00:22.000
Don't be nervous, I'm here

6
00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:27.833
Who is it? What are you doing at my house?

7
00:00:27.966 --> 00:00:28.900
Excuse me.

8
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:30.300
We're looking for two people.

9
00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:33.366
The man is in his 40s and the woman is in her 20s

10
00:00:33.366 --> 00:00:34.666
I don't know if you've seen it.

11
00:00:34.666 --> 00:00:37.166
Never seen me have to go to the toilet

12
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:38.433
Don't worry, ma'am

13
00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:41.166
Why are you looking for someone all night?

14
00:00:41.166 --> 00:00:42.400
Dry mouth

15
00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:44.300
Can you enjoy a glass of boiled water?

16
00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:47.333
No matter how deep the water is, you can quench your thirst.

17
00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:50.933
Okay, let me get you some water.

18
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:52.466
Since you are equal to waiting

19
00:00:52.466 --> 00:00:54.600
But you're done drinking and go

20
00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:55.900
Wait, I'm going to the toilet.

